snippet.title: Don't Starve: Reign of Giants Trailer |E3 2014 | PS4
snippet.description:
Trailer video for the "Reign of Giants" DLC for Don't Starve: Console Edition, coming soon to the Sony PS4. DLC will include new characters, new monsters, new items, and a more uncompromising world for the player to explore!

www.dontstarvegame.com
